@caption Alerts
The Alerts feature in Advanced Stock Tracker allows to you have emails 
sent to you when certain events occur in the security of your choosing. 
For example, you may wish to be notified when the price of a security 
reaches a set value or when it is no longer oversold. To get started, 
click the "New Alert" button on the left which will guide you through 
the process of creating an alert.
